I copied it out of her day-book
while she was away.

352
00:37:33.947 --> 00:37:35.906
Not nice. huh?

353
00:37:36.908 --> 00:37:40.119
Take care. I'm studying hard.

354
00:37:41.412 --> 00:37:42.580
Chikako.

355
00:37:48.253 --> 00:37:50.921
Hello! It's Hada.

356
00:38:09.149 --> 00:38:13.152
