511
00:53:23.939 --> 00:53:25.940
Lilico! Wait!

512
00:53:28.569 --> 00:53:29.527
Lilico!

513
00:53:29.653 --> 00:53:31.946
Kin-chan! Go after her!

514
00:53:32.072 --> 00:53:33.614
Lilico!

515
00:53:37.118 --> 00:53:39.203
I'm sick of this!

516
00:53:39.370 --> 00:53:41.956
