517
00:53:44.793 --> 00:53:47.962
You don't need me. right?

518
00:53:48.171 --> 00:53:51.090
You don't need me!

519
00:53:52.718 --> 00:53:54.719
I'm sick of it!

520
00:53:57.097 --> 00:54:00.600
