552
00:56:15.902 --> 00:56:18.278
I'll dump her and we can...

553
00:56:58.278 --> 00:56:59.529
Shin?

554
00:56:59.738 --> 00:57:00.905
Hi.

555
00:57:01.156 --> 00:57:02.322
